{"id": "ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 48, "displayName": {"text": "Still Life Ceramics Studio", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNEdFBYZkxnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Took the \"Bowl in One\" class. It's absolutely beginner-friendly, the instructor explains everything very clearly and takes you step by step through the whole process. It was my first experience with any ceramics class, and I had so much fun. Would definitely recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Took the \"Bowl in One\" class. It's absolutely beginner-friendly, the instructor explains everything very clearly and takes you step by step through the whole process. It was my first experience with any ceramics class, and I had so much fun. Would definitely recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Parangat Mittal", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114667540967548625554/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtceKrZnPDq2yBgDJAUfxlzBY3j4XhvKxBMdAvR0Jk6W3pTx513Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-03-25T01:16:57.491334Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNEdFBYZkxnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNEdFBYZkxnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c625784eb55f:0xbbe8bbd3aebf9087"}, {"name": "places/ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0aW9XSzNnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We went last night for the Bowl in One class with Aiden. It was super fun. My husband and I went to try something totally new. The studio is clean and full of inspiration. We met other fun people in class too. As a teacher for over 25 years, I can say that Aiden was an exceptional teacher and really made the experience. He was easy to follow and kind with all the newbies as we tried to figure it all out. I would definitely return with friends for another class. We're excited to head back in 3 weeks to pick up our final glazed and fired bowls. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We went last night for the Bowl in One class with Aiden. It was super fun. My husband and I went to try something totally new. The studio is clean and full of inspiration. We met other fun people in class too. As a teacher for over 25 years, I can say that Aiden was an exceptional teacher and really made the experience. He was easy to follow and kind with all the newbies as we tried to figure it all out. I would definitely return with friends for another class. We're excited to head back in 3 weeks to pick up our final glazed and fired bowls. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Aly", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110813261747502002987/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVg0iPSWGcDaa0GBaVxmts0gfuNlEFJrQlbBLn54H76RhrZLgA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-02-03T17:44:21.413980Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0aW9XSzNnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0aW9XSzNnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c625784eb55f:0xbbe8bbd3aebf9087"}, {"name": "places/ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQzel9hRFVREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Took a planters class here and had a great time. Originally I wanted to take a beginners but the instructions were concise and tailored to fit all levels. Ana was super helpful and accommodating. Got lucky with parking.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Took a planters class here and had a great time. Originally I wanted to take a beginners but the instructions were concise and tailored to fit all levels. Ana was super helpful and accommodating. Got lucky with parking.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Randi L Rubin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111459367325224700604/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf9_w_-227jviJo8GlH13Xe-0YSXuw25Sb4UE0VSwqUVYnwX_e=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2024-11-20T04:55:02.673249Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQzel9hRFVREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQzel9hRFVREAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c625784eb55f:0xbbe8bbd3aebf9087"}, {"name": "places/ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURud01ELVVnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I took a beginning wheel class five months ago and the hook got in deep. I took a 2nd class and then became a member. The studio has everything including really good music! The staff are wonderful, helpful and approachable. I've met good people. The studio has become a second home.\n\nTake a class and see what happens. Here's a photo of what I've been able to do after just a few short months.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I took a beginning wheel class five months ago and the hook got in deep. I took a 2nd class and then became a member. The studio has everything including really good music! The staff are wonderful, helpful and approachable. I've met good people. The studio has become a second home.\n\nTake a class and see what happens. Here's a photo of what I've been able to do after just a few short months.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Noah Stone", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102284550154500347152/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2d6V1Wq0UJjvONqpYn_WlB8HPqeu_v8OGWpg7qq153gafaj0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-01T22:46:49.280166Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURud01ELVVnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURud01ELVVnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c625784eb55f:0xbbe8bbd3aebf9087"}, {"name": "places/ChIJX7VOeCXGwoARh5C_rtO76Ls/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURIbXREcVNnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The supportive community at this studio is everything!! I got hooked after a Beginner’s Wheel class and never looked back. The studio is expansive and light-filled. The glaze room is phenomenal. I didn’t realize how lucky we were to have mid-fire AND high-fire (reduction) kilns. And the wealth of class & workshop options are always interesting.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The supportive community at this studio is everything!! I got hooked after a Beginner’s Wheel class and never looked back. The studio is expansive and light-filled. The glaze room is phenomenal. I didn’t realize how lucky we were to have mid-fire AND high-fire (reduction) kilns. And the wealth of class & workshop options are always interesting.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anne Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112204564169173079989/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe0aPN7g9XF0_YxXn1-avLU1XCMm77IRRX8DxF_xYK0pqTlENM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2024-09-14T20:27:33.035758Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURIbXREcVNnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURIbXREcVNnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c625784eb55f:0xbbe8bbd3aebf9087"}], "photos": [{"name":